<p><span class="anchor" id="p68"></span>الرُّجُوع فِي عينه مَا دَامَ بَاقِيا<a href="#p68" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p69"></span>فِي ملك الْمُقْتَرض<a href="#p69" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p70"></span>بِحَالَة<a href="#p70" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p71"></span>لم يتَعَلَّق بِهِ حق رهن أَو كِتَابَة أَو جِنَايَة<a href="#p71" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
